---
import PageHero from "../../../components/PageHero.astro";
import SAGPLayout from "../../../layouts/SAGPLayout.astro";
---

<SAGPLayout title="Distinguished Lectureship | SAGP">

<PageHero
  kicker="Distinguished Lectureship"
  title="Recognizing scholarship that has shaped the field."
  subtitle="Each year, SAGP honors a scholar whose work has made very substantial contributions to the study of Ancient Greek philosophy."
  image="/assets/images/parthenon_night.jpg"
/>

<section class="section two-col">
  <div>
    <h2>What is the Distinguished Lectureship?</h2>
  </div>

  <div>
    <p>
      The SAGP Distinguished Lecturer is chosen annually by the Board of
      Directors in recognition of very substantial contributions to scholarship
      in the field.
    </p>

    <p>
      The lectureship is a high professional distinction in its own right: an
      honor bestowed upon a scholar by their peers under the auspices of the
      Society for Ancient Greek Philosophy.
    </p>

    <div class="callout">
      The Distinguished Lectureship is not merely an event. It is one of the
      ways the Society recognizes and sustains excellence in Ancient Greek
      philosophy.
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section">
  <h2>Recent Distinguished Lectures</h2>

  <div class="card-grid">
    <article class="card">
      <h3>2025 · André Laks</h3>
      <p>
        “The kouros’ descent. A methodical reading of Parmenides’ route of search?”
      </p>
      <p><a href={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}/events/distinguished-lectureship/2025/`}>View the 2025 lecture</a></p>
    </article>

    <article class="card">
      <h3>2024 Distinguished Lecture</h3>
      <p>
        Details from the 2024 Distinguished Lectureship will be restored from
        the source archive.
      </p>
      <p><a href={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}/events/distinguished-lectureship/2024/`}>View the 2024 lecture</a></p>
    </article>

    <article class="card">
      <h3>Lecture Archive</h3>
      <p>
        The recent lectureship archive preserves a record of scholars honored
        by SAGP for significant contributions to the field.
      </p>
      <p><a href={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}/events/distinguished-lectureship/archive/`}>View the archive</a></p>
    </article>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section two-col">
  <div>
    <h2>A tradition of recognition</h2>
  </div>

  <div>
    <p>
      Through the Distinguished Lectureship, SAGP honors scholarship not only as
      individual achievement, but as a contribution to an ongoing community of
      inquiry.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

</SAGPLayout>
